---
title: Ultimate Springtime Salad with Crisp Radish, Snap Peas, and Fresh Mozzarella
description: What makes this salad ultimate? We’re not quite sure, exactly. It’s so much more than the sum of its parts! Herby pesto and fresh mozzarella might be a big part of it.
